,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:19:21.000Z","msg":"試下餵pinky撈螢養粉 <br />\n揀細隻啲pinky .....<br />\n同佢進補是必須的"},{"pid":"4780dbe97bbba1a33c1b71c36cdd423f786265a4","tid":17872,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:51:49.000Z","msg":"試下餵第種食物"},{"pid":"0a213f51c15fdbf8dd19720c9b4f1c56bb58e4d4","tid":17872,"uid":38585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:13:06.000Z","msg":"係咪唔夠熱消化唔到"},{"pid":"372898abe6ae64cca87745a499251287baf0fe2b","tid":17872,"uid":56162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"樓主隻野家下點？<br />\n我新買左兩隻都唔食野 好驚佢地會雙雙死去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6eb672b8bd1a99f2a34ac051b5f5bf0543a925","tid":17872,"uid":55321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:24:33.000Z","msg":"呢期轉天氣 我同我fd個兩隻都唔太開食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1c4ed551a30a20f7b4cb99a746f955b4ed072f","tid":17872,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網問唔識帶去睇醫生"},{"pid":"4b2e95b281aad85aca7ec065800661d9b9981b00","tid":17872,"uid":1172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T19:53:01.000Z","msg":"對上次柯d咩屎？有無尿酸出？平時餵乜？<br />\n無柯2 3星期建議睇獸醫<br />\n暫時keep住日日換水同放蟀同擺暗位唔好成日搞佢，暖毯放1/3控好d溫度"},{"pid":"a1487b5515d8d37c5a368e7932a9990ec6c60f80","tid":17872,"uid":9659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T20:45:45.000Z","msg":"香港人係咁，講到幾擔心幾擔心隻動物<br />\n又上網問又去鋪頭問<br />\n屌你既然咁擔心就去睇獸醫，咁易答到你就個個都做獸醫，啲鋪頭間間都開個獸醫部啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34b759a9b43e510792a547ed986ca7a91a65633","tid":17872,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T21:35:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e29537bfab9b7fd873e7af45a339e6f2cc2a131","tid":17872,"uid":9362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T21:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人係咁，講到幾擔心幾擔心隻動物<br />\n又上網問又去鋪頭問<br />\n屌你既然咁擔心就去睇獸醫，咁易答到你就個個都做獸醫，啲鋪頭間間都開個獸醫部啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔可以咁講，<br />\n有好多問題其實有簡單既解決方法，<br />\n即係你生粒暗瘡都唔會洗幾舊水睇醫生。<br />\n<br />\n而且爬蟲類算偏而且多種類，<br />\n有好多唔同既病症，<br />\n或者你以為係病，其實只係正常現象，<br />\n例如某d爬蟲冬天會唔食野幾個月。<br />\n<br />\n香港大部份獸醫都唔係專醫爬蟲，<br />\n多數都只係學到大路基本知識，<br />\n分分鐘經驗不及鋪頭同資深爬友，<br />\n上網問下無壞，真係無人答到先睇獸醫，<br />\nbtw你唔上網問睇怕你連香港有邊個專醫爬既獸醫都唔知"},{"pid":"4a0c22c563496fd2ac17e323492fec4c1c2dcbbc","tid":17872,"uid":62283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T18:16:13.000Z","msg":"有冇用溫控？溫控係必須<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975a6f2e7ffabef30588fcf2df3d62b4e5dccf9f","tid":17872,"uid":62283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T18:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻豹紋守宮已經冇屙屎差唔多兩星期 同冇食蟲兩三日 佢條尾仔就越黎越細 連行步路佢都好似好攰好頹咁 點解佢會咁？<br />\n有用暖氈，有鈣粉，買左益生菌溝水被佢飲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/115044_294c9aff16c1317be47c46820a0b43f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F115044_294c9aff16c1317be47c46820a0b43f8.jpg&h=65468171&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反轉個肚睇吓有冇啲黑色一堆係入面 睇返條尾未算好大獲 兩三日冇食都好小事 首要係check左溫度夠唔夠先"},{"pid":"eb9a2c0969ddeac260b2a74c392c384641e038bb","tid":17872,"uid":80168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我隻豹紋守宮已經冇屙屎差唔多兩星期 同冇食蟲兩三日 佢條尾仔就越黎越細 連行步路佢都好似好攰好頹咁 點解佢會咁？<br />\n有用暖氈，有鈣粉，買左益生菌溝水被佢飲<b